title: IntroGame
tags: #unused
---
Planet Renir
Gallo Sector
2678 Imperial Calendar
Vera Orion, a bounty hunter hired by House Trench to track down their kidnapped daughter, finds herself shipwrecked on a barren planet deep within the outer-ring colonies.
Alone with no communication to the rest of the empire, she discovers that the previous inhabitants of this jungle world are far from gone.
Locate 3 objects across the map to repair your ship.
===

